<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.230266>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 11. Apedunculata discoidea from ‘ curimatã-pacú’, Prochilodus argenteus from the São Francisco River, Brazil, in ventral view (5) Whole mount (composite). (6) Ventral bar (7) Dorsal bar. (8) Ventral anchor. (9) Dorsal anchor. (10) Copulatory complex. (11) Hook. Scale = 70 µm (1) and 25 µm (6 – 11)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/230266/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

